Name: Average resolution time following 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + In Call' activities in the log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Maximum time to reach 'Completed + In Call' from case start
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A50> - AppliesTo.PROCESS and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum duration between 'Completed + In Call' and any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Completed + In Call' to case closure
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Earliest occurrence of 'Completed + In Call' in a case lifecycle
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Latest occurrence of 'Completed + In Call' before case closure
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total active time of cases involving 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average lead time for cases with 'Completed + In Call' as the final activity before resolution
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest uninterrupted 'Completed + In Call' activity in a single case
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest time from case start to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average delay time before starting 'Completed + In Call' after 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Median duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total number of cases involving 'Completed + In Call' with a resolution time above average
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Duration variance of 'Completed + In Call' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Closed' compared to 'Completed + Resolved' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Distribution of 'Completed + In Call' duration across different organization countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Comparison of average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call' against 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time gap analysis between 'Completed + In Call' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'
